nvestigaci\\u00f3n cient\\u00edfica y human\\u00edstica editada por la Facultad de Estudios Superiores Acatl\\u00e1n-UNAM que publica, en espa\\u00f1ol o ingl\\u00e9s, art\\u00edculos originales, ensayos y rese\\u00f1as cr\\u00edticas en los cinco campos de conocimiento cultivados en la entidad, con los objetivos de intensificar la participaci\\u00f3n del di\\u00e1logo acad\\u00e9mico, contribuir en la con-figuraci\\u00f3n de la investigaci\\u00f3n b\\u00e1sica y aplicada y promover y difundir sus resultados en M\\u00e9xico y en el extranjero.<\\/p>"},"title":{"en_US":"Fig\\u016bras","es_ES":"Fig\\u016bras"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},"children":[],"_data":{"id":"176","menuId":"3","menuItemId":"25","parentId":"24","seq":"1"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},{"navigationMenuItem":{"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false,"_data":{"id":"26","contextId":"1","url":"","type":"NMI_TYPE_CUSTOM","path":"propositoyalcances","content":{"en_US":"<p><strong>Fig\\u016bras<\\/strong>: <strong>Research Academic Journal <\\/strong>is a triannual publication of scientific and humanistic research, edited by the Facultad de Estudios Superiores Acatl\\u00e1n-UNAM. It publishes, in either Spanish or English, original articles, essays and reviews on the five academic fields formed in the institution with the purposes of intensifying the sharing of academic discussion, contributing to the construction of basic and applied research, and promoting as well as disseminating its results in and out of Mexico.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Fig\\u016bras<\\/strong> is available online, in digital format, through open access files, looking forward to promoting research exchange.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Fig\\u016bras<\\/strong> evokes the act of transforming, tracing and representing in each publication the findings that authors lay on their articles.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Specialists with wide national and international recognition rigorously referee all of the manuscripts through open peer review (<a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/opr\\">OPR<\\/a>). Articles are published presenting studies in the following academic fields:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/arquitecturacomunicacionvisualmultimedia\\">Architecture and Visual and Multimedia Communication<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/humanidadesyartes\\">Humanities and Arts<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/cienciasjuridicas\\">Legal Sciences<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/matematicaseingenieria\\">Mathematics and Engineering<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/cienciassociales\\">Social Sciences<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","es_ES":"<p><strong><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">Fig\\u016bras: Revista acad\\u00e9mica de investigaci\\u00f3n<\\/span><\\/strong><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\"> es una publicaci\\u00f3n cuatrimestral de investigaci\\u00f3n cient\\u00edfica y human\\u00edstica editada por la Facultad de Estudios Superiores Acatl\\u00e1n-UNAM que publica, en espa\\u00f1ol o ingl\\u00e9s, art\\u00edculos originales, ensayos y rese\\u00f1as cr\\u00edticas en los cinco campos de conocimiento cultivados en la entidad, con los objetivos de intensificar la participaci\\u00f3n del di\\u00e1logo acad\\u00e9mico, contribuir en la con-figuraci\\u00f3n de la investigaci\\u00f3n b\\u00e1sica y aplicada y promover y difundir sus resultados en M\\u00e9xico y en el extranjero.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">Fig\\u016bras<\\/span><\\/strong><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\"> se encuentra disponible en formato digital para su consulta en archivos de acceso abierto con la finalidad de impulsar el intercambio de investigaciones.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Fig\\u016bras<\\/strong> evoca la acci\\u00f3n de transformar, delinear y representar en cada una de sus publicaciones, los hallazgos que cada participante plasma en sus art\\u00edculos.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>La totalidad de los manuscritos es rigurosamente arbitrada por especialistas con amplio reconocimiento nacional e internacional mediante el procedimiento de pares a revisi\\u00f3n abierta (<em><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/opr\\">Open Peer Review<\\/a><\\/em>); y los art\\u00edculos se publican en los siguientes campos de conocimiento:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/arquitecturacomunicacionvisualmultimedia\\">Arquitectura, Comunicaci\\u00f3n visual y Multimedia<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/cienciasjuridicas\\">Ciencias jur\\u00eddicas<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/cienciassociales\\">Ciencias sociales<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/humanidadesyartes\\">Humanidades y Artes<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/matematicaseingenieria\\">Matem\\u00e1ticas e Ingenier\\u00eda<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>"},"title":{"en_US":"Focus and Scope","es_ES":"Prop\\u00f3sito y alcances"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},"children":[],"_data":{"id":"177","menuId":"3","menuItemId":"26","parentId":"24","seq":"2"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},{"navigationMenuItem":{"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false,"_data":{"id":"27","contextId":"1","url":"","type":"NMI_TYPE_CUSTOM","path":"secciones","content":{"en_US":"<p><strong>Guidelines<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Perspectives (articles)<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Unpublished research articles that depict different aspects of academic inquiry, particularly in the following academic fields:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/arquitecturacomunicacionvisualmultimedia\\">Architecture, Visual and Multimedia Communication<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/humanidadesyartes\\">Humanities and Arts<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/cienciasjuridicas\\">Legal Sciences<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/matematicaseingenieria\\">Mathematics and Engineering<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/cienciassociales\\">Social Sciences<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>Manuscripts written by national and international researchers will be received in either Spanish or English.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Specialists with wide national and international recognition rigorously referee all of the manuscripts through open peer review (OPR).<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Scenarios (essays)<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Regulated dialogue of correlational questions where language is used and maintained to talk about a current issue. This by creating a linguistic setting in which the author and the reader are co-owners of an exchange of thoughts.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Essays will be from 6 to 10 pages long (1500-2500 words), and they will be received only by invitation of the responsible editor. [incorporar correo institucional de ensayo].<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>These texts will not be open peer reviewed (OPR).<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Resonances (critiques)<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Space dedicated to critical reviews of contemporary books that cover the journal\\u2019s disciplines and that encourage readers to reflect on the new directions of research.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Critiques will be no more than 4 pages long (1000 words) and they will be received only by invitation of the responsible editor. [incorporar correo institucional de ensayo].<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif; font-weight: normal;\\">These texts will not be open peer reviewed (OPR). <\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>","es_ES":"<p><strong>Lineamientos<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Perspectivas (art\\u00edculos)<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Art\\u00edculos de investigaci\\u00f3n in\\u00e9ditos que presenten diversos aspectos de la indagaci\\u00f3n acad\\u00e9mica, particularmente de los siguientes campos de conocimiento:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/arquitecturacomunicacionvisualmultimedia\\">Arquitectura, Comunicaci\\u00f3n visual y Multimedia<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/cienciasjuridicas\\">Ciencias jur\\u00eddicas<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/cienciassociales\\">Ciencias sociales<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/humanidadesyartes\\">Humanidades y Artes<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/matematicaseingenieria\\">Matem\\u00e1ticas e Ingenier\\u00eda<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>Los art\\u00edculos se recibir\\u00e1n tanto en ingl\\u00e9s como en espa\\u00f1ol, escritos por investigadores nacionales e internacionales.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>La totalidad de los manuscritos es rigurosamente arbitrada por especialistas con amplio reconocimiento nacional e internacional mediante el procedimiento de pares a revisi\\u00f3n abierta (<em>Open Peer Review<\\/em>).<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Escenas (ensayos)<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Di\\u00e1logo regulado de cuestionamientos rec\\u00edprocos donde se mantiene la pr\\u00e1ctica del lenguaje sobre un tema de la actualidad; es decir, se hace una escena ling\\u00fc\\u00edstica en la que el autor y el lector son copropietarios del intercambio de ideas.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Los ensayos tendr\\u00e1n una extensi\\u00f3n de entre 6 y 10 cuartillas (1500-2500 palabras), y se recibir\\u00e1n \\u00fanicamente mediante invitaci\\u00f3n del editor responsable [incorporar correo institucional de ensayo].<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Estos textos no ser\\u00e1n arbitrados.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Resonancias (rese\\u00f1as cr\\u00edticas)<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Espacio de cr\\u00edtica sobre libros recientes de las \\u00e1reas contempladas en la revista que propicien la reflexi\\u00f3n sobre los nuevos rumbos de la investigaci\\u00f3n.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>La extensi\\u00f3n no rebasar\\u00e1 las cuatro cuartillas (1000 palabras), y se recibir\\u00e1n \\u00fanicamente mediante invitaci\\u00f3n del editor responsable [incorporar correo institucional de ensayo].<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Estos textos no ser\\u00e1n arbitrados.<\\/p>"},"title":{"en_US":"Sections","es_ES":"Secciones"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},"children":[],"_data":{"id":"178","menuId":"3","menuItemId":"27","parentId":"24","seq":"3"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},{"navigationMenuItem":{"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false,"_data":{"id":"29","contextId":"1","url":"","type":"NMI_TYPE_CUSTOM","path":"politicadeaccesoabierto","content":{"en_US":"<p><strong>Fig\\u016bras<\\/strong>: <strong>Research Academic Journal<\\/strong> provides free and open access (user\\u2019s login and search). Additionally, all of the research documents\\u2019 publishing process stages are free of charge. This includes the reception of manuscripts, essays and critiques, the texts\\u2019 review and copyediting and, lastly, their publication in the journal.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The journal is published only in digital format. It owns a <a href=\\"https:\\/\\/creativecommons.org\\/licenses\\/by-nc\\/4.0\\/deed.es\\">Creative Commons license of the type Attribution-NonCommercial (by-nc)<\\/a> which means that the material can be publicly copied, used, disseminated transmitted and exposed, given that the journal\\u2019s <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/politicaseticasdepublicacion\\">Code of Ethics<\\/a> has been previously accepted and:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>The manuscript\'s authorship and the original source of its publication (the name of the journal and the URL or DOI of both the journal and the article) are mentioned.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>It is a non-profit work.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The existence and characteristics of this licensing agreement are indicated.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","es_ES":"<p><strong>Fig\\u016bras: Revista acad\\u00e9mica de investigaci\\u00f3n<\\/strong> proporciona acceso libre a sus secciones sin costo (registro de usuario y consulta), y tampoco cobra en ninguna fase del proceso de publicaci\\u00f3n de los trabajos de investigaci\\u00f3n: esto incluye la recepci\\u00f3n de los art\\u00edculos, de los ensayos y de las rese\\u00f1as; la dictaminaci\\u00f3n de los textos; la correcci\\u00f3n de estilo y, finalmente, la publicaci\\u00f3n digital en la revista.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>La revista se publica exclusivamente en formato digital. Ocupa una licencia <a href=\\"https:\\/\\/creativecommons.org\\/licenses\\/by-nc\\/4.0\\/deed.es\\">Creative Commons Reconocimiento-NoComercial (by-nc)<\\/a>. De esta manera, el material se puede copiar, usar, difundir, transmitir y exponer p\\u00fablicamente, siempre y cuando se haya aceptado el <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/politicaseticasdepublicacion\\">C\\u00f3digo de \\u00c9tica<\\/a> de la revista y:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\">Se mencione la autor\\u00eda del trabajo y la fuente original de su publicaci\\u00f3n (el nombre de la revista y el URL o DOI tanto de la revista como del art\\u00edculo).<\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\">No existan fines de lucro de por medio.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\">Se indique la existencia y caracter\\u00edsticas de este acuerdo de licencia<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>"},"title":{"en_US":"Open Access Policy","es_ES":"Pol\\u00edtica de acceso abierto"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},"children":[],"_data":{"id":"179","menuId":"3","menuItemId":"29","parentId":"24","seq":"4"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},{"navigationMenuItem":{"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false,"_data":{"id":"30","contextId":"1","url":"","type":"NMI_TYPE_CUSTOM","path":"resguardodelosarchivos","content":{"en_US":"<p><strong><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">Fig\\u016bras<\\/span><\\/strong><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">: <strong>Research Academic Journal<\\/strong> uses the LOCKSS system to generate one file distributed among the participating libraries, allowing the creation of the journal\\u2019s permanent files so they are preserved and restored.<\\/span><\\/p>","es_ES":"<p><strong><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">Fig\\u016bras: Revista acad\\u00e9mica de investigaci\\u00f3n<\\/span><\\/strong><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\"> utiliza el sistema LOCKSS para crear un archivo distribuido entre las bibliotecas participante, permitiendo a dichas bibliotecas crear archivos permanentes de la revista con fines de preservaci\\u00f3n y restauraci\\u00f3n. <\\/span><\\/p>"},"title":{"en_US":"Preservation of content","es_ES":"Resguardo de los archivos"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},"children":[],"_data":{"id":"180","menuId":"3","menuItemId":"30","parentId":"24","seq":"5"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},{"navigationMenuItem":{"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false,"_data":{"id":"31","contextId":"1","url":"","type":"NMI_TYPE_CUSTOM","path":"codigodeetica","content":{"en_US":"<p><strong>Fig\\u016bras<\\/strong>: <strong>Research Academic Journal<\\/strong> has a Code of Ethics to which all members of the editorial team, authors and reviewers must adhere. For further information, go to:&nbsp;<a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/politicaseticasdepublicacion\\">Code of Ethics<\\/a>.<\\/p>","es_ES":"<p><strong>Fig\\u016bras: Revista acad\\u00e9mica de investigaci\\u00f3n<\\/strong> tiene un C\\u00f3digo de \\u00c9tica al cual se adhieren todos los miembros del equipo editorial, autores y dictaminadores. Para m\\u00e1s informaci\\u00f3n, consultar: <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/politicaseticasdepublicacion\\">C\\u00f3digo de \\u00e9tica<\\/a>.<\\/p>"},"title":{"en_US":"Code of Ethics","es_ES":"C\\u00f3digo de \\u00e9tica"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},"children":[],"_data":{"id":"181","menuId":"3","menuItemId":"31","parentId":"24","seq":"6"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},{"navigationMenuItem":{"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false,"_data":{"id":"32","contextId":"1","url":"","type":"NMI_TYPE_CUSTOM","path":"plagio","content":{"en_US":"<p><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">All manuscripts submitted to <strong>Fig\\u016bras<\\/strong>: <strong>Research Academic Journal<\\/strong> will be reviewed by using different plagiarism detection tools. Those articles in which plagiarism, self-plagiarism, doubtful citation and the guidelines indicated in the <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/politicaseticasdepublicacion\\"><span style=\\"color: #e26627;\\">Code of Ethics<\\/span><\\/a> have been identified will be rejected. <\\/span><\\/p>","es_ES":"<p><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">Todos los manuscritos enviados a la <strong>Fig\\u016bras: Revista acad\\u00e9mica de investigaci\\u00f3n<\\/strong> ser\\u00e1n revisados utilizando diversas herramientas de detecci\\u00f3n de plagio. Se rechazar\\u00e1n los art\\u00edculos en que se detecte plagio, auto-plagio, dudosa citaci\\u00f3n y las normas que indica el <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/politicaseticasdepublicacion\\"><span style=\\"color: #e26627;\\">C\\u00f3digo de \\u00e9tica<\\/span><\\/a> de la revista. <\\/span><\\/p>"},"title":{"en_US":"Plagiarism","es_ES":"Plagio"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},"children":[],"_data":{"id":"182","menuId":"3","menuItemId":"32","parentId":"24","seq":"7"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false}],"_data":{"id":"175","menuId":"3","menuItemId":"24","parentId":"0","seq":"0"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},{"navigationMenuItem":{"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false,"_data":{"id":"33","contextId":"1","url":"","type":"NMI_TYPE_CUSTOM","path":"comopublicar","content":{"en_US":"<p><strong>Fig\\u016bras<\\/strong><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">: <\\/span><strong>Research Academic Journal <\\/strong><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">is a triannual publication of scientific and humanistic research, edited by the Facultad de Estudios Superiores Acatl\\u00e1n, UNAM. It publishes, in either Spanish or English, original articles, essays and reviews on the five academic fields formed in the institution with the purpose of intensifying the sharing of academic discussion, contributing to the construction of basic and applied research, and promoting and disseminating its results in and out of Mexico. <\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Fig\\u016bras is available online, in digital format, through XML and PDF open access files, looking forward to promoting research exchange.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Fig\\u016bras evokes the act of transforming, tracing and representing in each publication the findings that authors lay on their articles. <\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">The topics and research of the manuscripts must have high quality and originality. Manuscripts can be written in Spanish and <\\/span><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">English covering topics of any of the following academic fields:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">[Insertar v\\u00ednculos a las instrucciones de cada \\u00e1rea]<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\" style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Architecture and Visual and Multimedia Communication<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\" style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Humanities and Arts<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\" style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Legal Sciences<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\" style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Mathematics and Engineering<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\" style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Social Sciences<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","es_ES":""},"title":{"en_US":"How to submit","es_ES":"\\u00bfC\\u00f3mo publicar?"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},"children":[{"navigationMenuItem":{"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false,"_data":{"id":"35","contextId":"1","url":"","type":"NMI_TYPE_CUSTOM","path":"criteriosyprocedimientoseditoriales","content":{"en_US":"<p><strong><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">Fig\\u016bras<\\/span><\\/strong><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">: <strong>Research Academic Journal <\\/strong>is a triannual publication of scientific and humanistic research, edited by the Facultad de Estudios Superiores Acatl\\u00e1n-UNAM. It publishes, in either Spanish or English, original articles, essays and reviews on the five academic fields formed in the institution, with the purposes of intensifying the sharing of academic discussion, contributing to the construction of basic and applied research, and promoting as well as disseminating its results in and out of Mexico.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">Fig\\u016bras is available online, in digital format, through XML and PDF open access files, looking forward to promoting research exchange.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">Fig\\u016bras evokes the act of transforming, tracing and representing in each publication the findings that authors lay on their articles.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">The topics and research of the manuscripts must have high quality and originality. Manuscripts can be written in either Spanish or English covering topics of any of the following academic fields:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/arquitecturacomunicacionvisualmultimedia\\">Architecture, Visual and Multimedia Communication<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/humanidadesyartes\\">Humanities and Arts<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/cienciasjuridicas\\">Legal Sciences<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/matematicaseingenieria\\">Mathematics and Engineering<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/cienciassociales\\">Social Sciences<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/procedimientoeditorial\\">Publishing process<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/revisionabiertaporpares\\">Open Peer Review (OPR)<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/aceptacion\\">Acceptance<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","es_ES":"<p style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\\"><strong><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">Fig\\u016bras: Revista acad\\u00e9mica de investigaci\\u00f3n <\\/span><\\/strong><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">es una publicaci\\u00f3n cuatrimestral de investigaci\\u00f3n cient\\u00edfica y human\\u00edstica editada por la Facultad de Estudios Superiores Acatl\\u00e1n-UNAM que publica, en espa\\u00f1ol o ingl\\u00e9s, art\\u00edculos originales, ensayos y rese\\u00f1as cr\\u00edticas en los cinco campos de conocimiento cultivados en la entidad, con los objetivos de intensificar la participaci\\u00f3n del di\\u00e1logo acad\\u00e9mico, contribuir en la configuraci\\u00f3n de la investigaci\\u00f3n b\\u00e1sica y aplicada y promover y difundir sus resultados en M\\u00e9xico y en el extranjero.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">Fig\\u016bras se encuentra disponible en formato digital para su consulta en archivos de acceso abierto en formato XML y PDF con la finalidad de impulsar el intercambio de investigaciones.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">Fig\\u016bras evoca la acci\\u00f3n de transformar, delinear y representar en cada una de sus publicaciones, los hallazgos que cada participante plasma en sus art\\u00edculos.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">Los temas e investigaciones de los art\\u00edculos deben ser originales y de profunda calidad en la investigaci\\u00f3n. Los art\\u00edculos pueden estar escritos en espa\\u00f1ol o ingl\\u00e9s y podr\\u00e1n abordar temas de cualquiera de los siguientes campos de conocimiento:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/arquitecturacomunicacionvisualmultimedia\\">Arquitectura, Comunicaci\\u00f3n Visual y Multimedia<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/cienciasjuridicas\\">Ciencias jur\\u00eddicas<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/cienciassociales\\">Ciencias sociales<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/humanidadesyartes\\">Humanidades y Artes<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/matematicaseingenieria\\">Matem\\u00e1ticas e Ingenier\\u00eda<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/procedimientoeditorial\\">Procedimiento editorial<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/revisionabiertaporpares\\">Revisi\\u00f3n abierta por pares (open peer review, OPR)<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/aceptacion\\">Aceptaci\\u00f3n<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>"},"title":{"en_US":"Editorial criteria and procedures","es_ES":"Criterios y procedimientos editoriales"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},"children":[],"_data":{"id":"184","menuId":"3","menuItemId":"35","parentId":"33","seq":"9"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},{"navigationMenuItem":{"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false,"_data":{"id":"36","contextId":"1","url":"","type":"NMI_TYPE_CUSTOM","path":"opr","content":{"en_US":"<p>The type of review to be used is open peer review (OPR) from only one of the reviewers. This means that three reviewers will submit their evaluations of each of the manuscripts anonymously and, by an open computational procedure, one of them will be revealed in order to interact with the author, if necessary.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>In this way, the names of the authors and two of the reviewers are not disclosed and just one of the evaluations is known. Thus, this system keeps the integrity of open access and open data procedures, and provides certainty to the peer-reviewing process.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Once the reviewers accept the procedure and the manuscript, they will examine it carefully according to their field of specialization and the publishing guidelines of <strong>Fig\\u016bras. <\\/strong>Then, they will send the opinion with either the acknowledgement (including suggestions for change) or the denial of its publication.<\\/p>","es_ES":"<p style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">El tipo de revisi\\u00f3n de los art\\u00edculos ser\\u00e1 por pares a revisi\\u00f3n abierta (open peer review, OPR) de uno de los tres dictaminadores; es decir, para cada art\\u00edculo habr\\u00e1 tres revisores que entregar\\u00e1n sus dict\\u00e1menes an\\u00f3nimamente y, por un proceso aleatorio computacional, se realizar\\u00e1 la apertura de una de las identidades de los revisores que podr\\u00e1 interactuar con el autor si \\u00e9ste lo solicita.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"western\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">De esta manera, los nombres de los autores y dos de los dictaminadores no ser\\u00e1n revelados y s\\u00f3lo una de las evaluaciones podr\\u00e1 ser conocida. Esta forma de revisi\\u00f3n mantiene el esp\\u00edritu de acceso abierto (Open Access) y datos abiertos (Open Data), y busca dar mayor certidumbre al sistema de arbitraje de revistas internacionales.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"western\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">Una vez que los dictaminadores acepten el procedimiento y el art\\u00edculo, examinar\\u00e1n el manuscrito rigurosamente de acuerdo con su especialidad y los criterios de publicaci\\u00f3n de <strong>Fig\\u016bras<\\/strong> para posteriormente enviar el dictamen con la recomendaci\\u00f3n para su publicaci\\u00f3n (con las sugerencias de los cambios pertinentes) o la conveniencia de no publicarlo.<\\/span><\\/p>"},"title":{"en_US":"Open Peer Review (OPR)","es_ES":"Revisi\\u00f3n por pares (open peer review, OPR)"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},"children":[],"_data":{"id":"185","menuId":"3","menuItemId":"36","parentId":"33","seq":"10"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},{"navigationMenuItem":{"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false,"_data":{"id":"37","contextId":"1","url":"","type":"NMI_TYPE_CUSTOM","path":"manualdereferencias","content":{"en_US":"<p>References according to <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.chicagomanualofstyle.org\\/home.html\\">The Chicago Manual of Style 17th Edition<\\/a> .<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Formats are divided into:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\">Author-date. It is used to cite the author in parenthesis. The complete information is written in the references.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\">Notes and bibliography. It is used to refer specific notes in the text and footnotes. Data is found complete in the bibliography.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>It is preferable to add the DOI for online books and articles. Nonetheless, when this information is unknown, the URL can be used instead.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>In order to avoid any difficulty in its retrieval, it was decided to omit the period after the URL (and DOI) in all references. This exception will apply for the digital and PDF versions of the article.<\\/p>\\r\\n<dl>\\r\\n<dt class=\\"show\\">Journal articles<\\/dt>\\r\\n<dt class=\\"show\\">Online articles<\\/dt>\\r\\n<dt class=\\"show\\">Books<\\/dt>\\r\\n<dd class=\\"show\\">Printed<\\/dd>\\r\\n<dd class=\\"show\\">Online<\\/dd>\\r\\n<dd class=\\"show\\">eBook<\\/dd>\\r\\n<dt class=\\"show\\">Websites<\\/dt>\\r\\n<dt class=\\"show\\">Audiovisual and other multimedia (recordings, app content, songs, albums, videos, audiobooks, TV Series, podcasts, etc. including online resources)<\\/dt>\\r\\n<dt class=\\"show\\">Blogs<\\/dt>\\r\\n<dt class=\\"show\\">Magazines or newspapers<\\/dt>\\r\\n<dt class=\\"show\\">Artworks<\\/dt>\\r\\n<dd class=\\"show\\">Paintings, photographs, sculptures, or other works of art<\\/dd>\\r\\n<dd class=\\"show\\">Tables and figures<\\/dd>\\r\\n<dt class=\\"show\\">Social media content<\\/dt>\\r\\n<\\/dl>\\r\\n<p><a class=\\"obj_galley_link pdf\\" style=\\"color: #007ab2; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #007ab2; display: inline-block; padding: 0 1em; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 28px; text-decoration: none;\\" href=\\"\\/ojs\\/public\\/journals\\/1\\/descargas\\/References_FINAL.pdf\\" rel=\\"noopener\\" download=\\"Reference Manual of Fig\\u016bras\\"> PDF<\\/a><\\/p>","es_ES":"<p>Las referencias de los art\\u00edculos se elaborar\\u00e1n de acuerdo a <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.chicagomanualofstyle.org\\/home.html\\">The Chicago Manual of Style 17th Edition<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>El formato est\\u00e1 dividido en:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\">Autor-fecha. Se ocupa para citar al autor mediante par\\u00e9ntesis. Los datos de la cita se ampl\\u00edan en las referencias.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\">Notas y bibliograf\\u00eda. Se emplea para llamadas en el texto y notas al pie de p\\u00e1gina. Los datos se completan en la bibliograf\\u00eda.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>Se preferir\\u00e1 ocupar el DOI para los libros y art\\u00edculos en l\\u00ednea; en caso de no contar con \\u00e9l, se pondr\\u00e1 el URL.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Se decidi\\u00f3 que no se pondr\\u00e1 punto al final de direcciones electr\\u00f3nicas (tanto DOI como URL) en las referencias para que no se vea imposibilitada su consulta; esta excepci\\u00f3n se ocupar\\u00e1 para la versi\\u00f3n digital y PDF de los art\\u00edculos.<\\/p>\\r\\n<dl>\\r\\n<dt class=\\"show\\">Art\\u00edculos de revistas acad\\u00e9micas<\\/dt>\\r\\n<dt class=\\"show\\">Art\\u00edculos en l\\u00ednea<\\/dt>\\r\\n<dt class=\\"show\\">Libros<\\/dt>\\r\\n<dd class=\\"show\\">Impresos<\\/dd>\\r\\n<dd class=\\"show\\">En l\\u00ednea<\\/dd>\\r\\n<dd class=\\"show\\">E-book<\\/dd>\\r\\n<dt class=\\"show\\">Websites<\\/dt>\\r\\n<dt class=\\"show\\">Recursos audiovisuales y multimedia (grabaciones, contenido digital, canciones, videos, CD, audiolibros, series de televisi\\u00f3n, pel\\u00edculas, podcasts, etc., incluyendo contenido en l\\u00ednea)<\\/dt>\\r\\n<dt class=\\"show\\">Blogs<\\/dt>\\r\\n<dt class=\\"show\\">Revistas y peri\\u00f3dicos<\\/dt>\\r\\n<dt class=\\"show\\">Ilustraciones<\\/dt>\\r\\n<dd class=\\"show\\">Pinturas, fotograf\\u00edas, esculturas y otras piezas de arte<\\/dd>\\r\\n<dd class=\\"show\\">Tablas y figuras<\\/dd>\\r\\n<dt class=\\"show\\">Redes sociales<\\/dt>\\r\\n<\\/dl>\\r\\n<p><a class=\\"obj_galley_link pdf\\" style=\\"color: #007ab2; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #007ab2; display: inline-block; padding: 0 1em; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 28px; text-decoration: none;\\" href=\\"\\/ojs\\/public\\/journals\\/1\\/descargas\\/Referencias_FINAL.pdf\\" rel=\\"noopener\\" download=\\"Manual de Referencias de Fig\\u016bras\\"> PDF<\\/a><\\/p>"},"title":{"en_US":"Reference Manual of  Fig\\u016bras","es_ES":"Manual de Referencias de Fig\\u016bras"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},"children":[],"_data":{"id":"186","menuId":"3","menuItemId":"37","parentId":"33","seq":"11"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},{"navigationMenuItem":{"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false,"_data":{"id":"38","contextId":"1","url":"","type":"NMI_TYPE_CUSTOM","path":"politicaseticasdepublicacion","content":{"en_US":"<p><strong>Code of Ethics<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>In order to submit a manuscript, it is necessary for each author to carefully read the Code of Ethics, and send it signed in a PDF file.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em>Code of Ethics<\\/em><br><br><a class=\\"obj_galley_link pdf\\" style=\\"color: #007ab2; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #007ab2; display: inline-block; padding: 0 1em; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 28px; text-decoration: none;\\" href=\\"\\/ojs\\/public\\/journals\\/1\\/descargas\\/CodeEthics_15ene2019.pdf\\" download=\\"Code of Ethics\\">PDF<\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Privacy Statement<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>All information provided to <strong>Fig\\u016bras: Research Academic Journal <\\/strong>will be exclusively used for the established purposes, and will not be given to third parties for its use with any other intentions.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Copyright<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Texts published in <strong>Fig\\u016bras: Research Academic Journal <\\/strong>are subject to the following regulations:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\">Authors retain the copyright and grant, non-exclusively, the exploitation rights of accepted works for its publication in <strong>Fig\\u016bras: Research Academic Journal, <\\/strong>giving to the journal the guarantee of being the first one to publish such work.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\">All manuscripts are published exclusively online under a <a href=\\"https:\\/\\/creativecommons.org\\/licenses\\/by-nc\\/4.0\\/deed.es\\">Creative Commons license of the type Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International (by-nc)<\\/a>. In this way, articles can be publicly copied, used, disseminated, transmitted and exposed, provided that:<\\/li>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\">The manuscript\\u2019s authorship and the original source of its publication are mentioned (journal\\u2019s editor and URL of the document).<\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\">It is a non-profit work.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\">The existence and characteristics of this license agreement are mentioned.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\">Self-archive conditions. The electronic dissemination, by the authors, of the Preprint version of the article in prestigious repositories before its final publication is allowed, on condition that they refer to its publication in <strong>Fig\\u016bras: Research Academic Journal<\\/strong>. This will contribute to the previous dissemination so as to encourage a broader scope among the academic community.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","es_ES":"<p><strong><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">C\\u00f3digo de \\u00e9tica<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">Para proponer un trabajo de investigaci\\u00f3n, es necesario que cada autor lea detenidamente el C\\u00f3digo de \\u00c9tica y lo env\\u00ede firmado en PDF.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\\"><em><span style=\\"font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif;\\">C\\u00f3digo de \\u00e9tica<\\/span><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\\"><br><a class=\\"obj_galley_link pdf\\" style=\\"color: #007ab2; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #007ab2; display: inline-block; padding: 0 1em; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 28px; text-decoration: none;\\" href=\\"\\/ojs\\/public\\/journals\\/1\\/descargas\\/CodigoEtica_110119_FINAL.pdf\\" download=\\"C\\u00f3digo de \\u00c9tica\\">PDF<\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Declaraci\\u00f3n de privacidad<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Todos los datos proporcionados a <strong>Fig\\u016bras: Revista acad\\u00e9mica de investigaci\\u00f3n <\\/strong>se usar\\u00e1n exclusivamente para los fines declarados en ella y no se proporcionar\\u00e1n por ning\\u00fan motivo a terceros ni para su uso con otros fines.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Aviso de derechos de autor<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Los textos publicados en <strong>Fig\\u016bras: Revista acad\\u00e9mica de investigaci\\u00f3n <\\/strong>est\\u00e1n sujetos a lo siguiente:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\">Los autores conservan los derechos de autor y ceden de forma no exclusiva los derechos de explotaci\\u00f3n de los trabajos aceptados para su publicaci\\u00f3n en <strong>Fig\\u016bras: Revista acad\\u00e9mica de investigaci\\u00f3n<\\/strong>, garantizando a la revista el derecho a ser la primera en publicar dicho trabajo.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\">Los trabajos se publican exclusivamente de manera electr\\u00f3nica bajo una licencia <a href=\\"https:\\/\\/creativecommons.org\\/licenses\\/by-nc\\/4.0\\/deed.es\\">Creative Commons Reconocimiento-NoComercial (by-nc)<\\/a>. De esta manera, los trabajos se pueden copiar, usar, difundir, transmitir y exponer p\\u00fablicamente, siempre y cuando:<\\/li>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\">Se mencione la autor\\u00eda del trabajo y la fuente original de su publicaci\\u00f3n (editor de revistas y la URL de la obra).<\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\">No existan fines de lucro de por medio.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\">Se mencione la existencia y caracter\\u00edsticas de este acuerdo de licencia.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\">Condiciones de auto-archivo. Se permite que los autores difundan electr\\u00f3nicamente la versi\\u00f3n Preprint de sus trabajos en repositorios de reconocido prestigio antes de su publicaci\\u00f3n definitiva, haciendo referencia a su publicaci\\u00f3n en <strong>Fig\\u016bras: Revista acad\\u00e9mica de investigaci\\u00f3n<\\/strong>. De esta manera se favorece la difusi\\u00f3n previa para que exista un mayor alcance entre la comunidad acad\\u00e9mica.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\">&nbsp;<\\/p>"},"title":{"en_US":"Publication ethics","es_ES":"Pol\\u00edticas \\u00e9ticas de publicaci\\u00f3n"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},"children":[],"_data":{"id":"187","menuId":"3","menuItemId":"38","parentId":"33","seq":"12"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false}],"_data":{"id":"183","menuId":"3","menuItemId":"33","parentId":"0","seq":"8"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},{"navigationMenuItem":{"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false,"_data":{"id":"34","contextId":"1","url":"","type":"NMI_TYPE_CUSTOM","path":"directorio","content":{"en_US":"","es_ES":""},"title":{"en_US":"Editorial Staff","es_ES":"Directorio"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},"children":[],"_data":{"id":"188","menuId":"3","menuItemId":"34","parentId":"0","seq":"13"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[]